Class BatchRequestsFactory<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • batchrequests.BatchRequestsFactory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the request to be batched.

    public class BatchRequestsFactory<T>
extends Object
    Convenience factory to generate a BatchSubmitter. Create a factory using BatchRequestsFactory.BatchRequestsFactoryBuilder.
